"Do you want to save your changes as a draft?" = "Kas soovid muudatused mustandina salvestada?";

"Are you sure you want to unfollow this planet?" = "Kas soovid kindlasti selle planeedi jälgimise lõpetada?";

"Here are your archived Planets. Archived planets are not auto published or updated. You can unarchive them from here." = "Siin on sinu arhiveeritud planeedid. Arhiveeritud planeete ei avaldata ega värskendata automaatselt. Siit saad need arhiivist taastada.";


"Are you sure you want to delete %@? This action cannot be undone." = "Kas soovid kindlasti kustutada %@? Seda toimingut ei saa tagasi võtta.";

"Are you sure you want to delete this post?\n\n%@?\n\nThis action cannot be undone." = "Kas soovid kindlasti selle postituse kustutada?\n\n%@?\n\nSeda toimingut ei saa tagasi võtta.";

"Would you like to use new library location at" = "Kas soovid kasutada uut teegi asukohta:";

"current database including following planets will be replaced with contents at this location" = "praegune andmebaas koos jälgitavate planeetidega asendatakse selle asukoha sisuga";

"When you tip a creator, transactions will be sent to the selected Ethereum network." = "Kui toetad loojat, saadetakse tehingud valitud Ethereumi võrku.";

"Are you sure you want to archive this planet? Archived planets will not be auto updated. You can later unarchive it from settings." = "Kas soovid kindlasti selle planeedi arhiveerida? Arhiveeritud planeete ei värskendata automaatselt. Saad selle hiljem sätetest arhiivist taastada.";

"Planet lets you build and host your website on your Mac without requiring a centralized service." = "Planet võimaldab sul oma veebisaiti Macis luua ja majutada ilma keskset teenust vajamata.";

"You can also use Planet to follow the content creators you like." = "Saad Planetit kasutada ka meeldivate sisuloojate jälgimiseks.";

"The big difference is that there is no middle layer between you and the content creators you follow." = "Suur erinevus on see, et sinu ja jälgitavate sisuloojate vahel pole vahendajat.";

"You will receive the latest updates in a peer-to-peer manner." = "Saad uusimad värskendused võrdõigusvõrgu kaudu.";

"The slug is the part of the URL that identifies the article. It should be unique and contain only lowercased letters, numbers, and hyphens." = "Slug on URL-i osa, mis tuvastab artikli. See peab olema kordumatu ning sisaldama ainult väiketähti, numbreid ja sidekriipse.";

"If you want this article to redirect to an external link, enter the URL here." = "Kui soovid, et see artikkel suunaks välisele lingile, sisesta URL siia.";

"This domain will be used in places that need a domain prefix, like for RSS or Podcast feeds." = "Seda domeeni kasutatakse kohtades, kus on vaja domeeniprefiksit, näiteks RSS-i või taskuhäälingu voogudes.";

"Are you sure you want to archive this planet? Archived planets will not be auto published. You can later unarchive it from settings." = "Kas soovid kindlasti selle planeedi arhiveerida? Arhiveeritud planeete ei avaldata automaatselt. Saad selle hiljem sätetest arhiivist taastada.";

"Please input an integer for sorting, entries with smaller numbers will be ranked first." = "Sisesta sortimiseks täisarv; väiksema numbriga kirjed järjestatakse ettepoole.";

"Articles of the Page type are not listed on the blog index page, nor are they included in the RSS feed." = "Lehe tüüpi artikleid ei kuvata blogi avalehel ega lisata RSS-voogu.";

"Are you sure you want to delete this article? This action will remove it from your feed. However, if the article is still available on the source, it will reappear in your feed the next time you refresh it." = "Kas soovid kindlasti selle artikli kustutada? See toiming eemaldab selle sinu voost. Kui artikkel on allikas endiselt saadaval, ilmub see järgmisel värskendamisel uuesti voogu.";


